data.description:
Look at this stunning farmhouse! This spacious property is situated on 45 acres. This home has 4 bedrooms and 3 bathrooms, and 2 living spaces. The living room features a cozy wood burning stove, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere for family gatherings and entertaining. This property has a lot of mature trees, including pecan, peach and pear trees! There are two ponds located on the property. This property includes a small shop that is well insulated and has electric, there is a big barn that has electric, a shop for all your working needs including 220 plugs. There is also an additional structure that’s perfect for animals and a loading shoot. The back half of the property has been sprayed you can bail hay on approximately 26 acres. Don’t miss out on the opportunity to make this property your home!
**Additional 8 acres is also available**
